/* Level countdown clock (top-left, under the PLANETFALL title).
   Shared by Level 1 (#countdown), the Drone Bay (#db-countdown), and the
   shelved Archive level (#l2-countdown). */
#countdown,
#l2-countdown,
#db-countdown,
